About
House Of  Henry was envisioned, designed, stocked, and staffed with one mission in mind: to bring you great food and beer. We hope you enjoy the friendly atmosphere here at Florida’s most authentic Irish pub. However, any establishment is merely bricks and mortar without the people that create the atmosphere. The HOH is blessed with the finest staff. So belly on up to the bar, grab a stool, order a pint (or your preference) and experience some Irish hospitality. Thank you for the privilege of serving you.
We feature a quick and satisfying lunch including daily specials. Stop by after work for one of the best happy hours in town.
Good people drink good beer.
Hunter S. Thompson
